WEBVTT

00:00:26.522 --> 00:00:27.455
yo.

00:00:27.455 --> 00:00:28.674
shoyn?

00:00:28.041 --> 00:00:33.199
mir hobn, mir hobn geendikt, un men halt, ir hot ongehoybn...

00:00:31.602 --> 00:00:35.747
ven m'hot undz farnemen arbetn in, tsu, tsu di koyln.

00:00:33.863 --> 00:00:35.226
⟨oy⟩f koyln.

00:00:35.226 --> 00:00:36.169
yo.

00:00:35.955 --> 00:00:41.636
nu, m'iz gekumen, hot ge- m'hot gezogt in, Popovets, az mir zol'mir geyn arbetn, nu.

00:00:41.811 --> 00:00:45.275
ho'mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen az fun undz darf yeder geyn,

00:00:45.275 --> 00:00:46.546
ale fir.

00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.246
 ze'mir gegangen.

00:00:51.531 --> 00:00:56.792
in Popovets, hintn, ho'mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen. drum hot men undz in vagonen arayngevarfn,

00:00:56.792 --> 00:01:02.729
azoyne vi, beheymes. me firt in di vagonen: f⟨u⟩l, tsu fuftsik mentshn in a vagon,

00:01:02.736 --> 00:01:04.620
un mir ze'mir geforn.

00:01:05.031 --> 00:01:09.564
di ershte OSTANOVKA, gedenk ikh, iz geven in Zhmerinke.

00:01:10.735 --> 00:01:16.283
shtark a sheyne geven dortn di stantsye mit alemen in Zhmerinke.

00:01:16.283 --> 00:01:18.636
undz ze'mir geshtanen lang.

00:01:19.088 --> 00:01:22.164
esn un trinken hot men undz gornisht gegibn.

00:01:22.164 --> 00:01:23.385
m'iz geforn

00:01:23.965 --> 00:01:28.552
arbetn. azoy ken men arbetn az me hot nisht keyn esn? vu nemt men koyekh?

00:01:28.552 --> 00:01:29.899
nor dos iz...

00:01:29.955 --> 00:01:32.362
ze'mir gezesn in dem vagon

00:01:33.229 --> 00:01:39.517
un s'iz geven f- in der fri. voser a tog, veys ikh nisht, nor ikh, dos gedenk ikh shtark gut.

00:01:40.283 --> 00:01:42.065
iz, in der fri

00:01:42.915 --> 00:01:45.115
hob ikh shtark gevolt trinken.

00:01:45.115 --> 00:01:46.234
vaser?

00:01:46.763 --> 00:01:49.029
s'iz geven farshlosn di vagonen.

00:01:49.029 --> 00:01:52.057
ze'mir ge- he, gezesn dort in di vagon.

00:01:52.057 --> 00:01:55.214
geven a kleyn fentsterl, hob ikh oyfgehoybn zikh

00:01:55.214 --> 00:01:59.939
un gehaltn ofn dos moyl, vayl s'iz mir geven fartriknt in moyl far a kap vaser.

00:01:59.939 --> 00:02:02.248
etlekhe tog keyn vaser nisht gehat.

00:02:03.081 --> 00:02:05.674
 un gib a kuk: oyf der anderer zayt

00:02:05.680 --> 00:02:07.575
shteyt a poyezd

00:02:07.575 --> 00:02:08.745
mit daytshn.

00:02:09.038 --> 00:02:10.899
hob ikh mikh dershrokn.

00:02:10.899 --> 00:02:12.491
un oyfn,

00:02:12.497 --> 00:02:15.492
azoy ⟨s-⟩ iz geshtanen lebn vagon,

00:02:15.492 --> 00:02:17.351
iz geshtanen a daytsh,

00:02:17.357 --> 00:02:19.612
mitl-yorn a mentsh.

00:02:19.618 --> 00:02:21.755
er hot mikh gegibn a derze.

00:02:22.352 --> 00:02:24.180
hot er epes gezogt,

00:02:24.180 --> 00:02:27.605
hob ikh mikh teykef farbahaltn arayn krik, vayl kh'hob moyre gehat.

00:02:27.605 --> 00:02:31.586
fregt der bruder, "vos iz geshen?" zog ikh, "epes a daytsh redt tsu mir."

00:02:31.586 --> 00:02:34.685
zogt er, "er vet dir gornisht tun. lomir gibn a kuk."

00:02:34.685 --> 00:02:37.326
a klal, kukt er aroys, un ikh.

00:02:37.455 --> 00:02:38.675
fregt er

00:02:38.675 --> 00:02:42.388
dem bruder, "vos iz mit di MÄDCHEN? vos veynt zi?"

00:02:42.315 --> 00:02:44.391
 in DEUTSCH⟨UNK⟩n loshn?

00:02:43.864 --> 00:02:47.159
yo. ikh hob nisht gekent ⟨DEUTSCH⟩, nor kh'hob di verter,

00:02:47.159 --> 00:02:49.070
gedenk ikh ale yorn.

00:02:49.070 --> 00:02:51.709
zogt der bruder, "zi vil WASSER."

00:02:53.470 --> 00:02:58.672
vos hot er gezogt? "a SCHADE aza MÄDCHEN, a groyse SCHADE.

00:02:58.672 --> 00:03:04.854
ikh breng.", er hot gezogt. iker, s'hot gedoyert nisht keyn sakh. er iz tsugekumen mit a fuln kesl vaser.

00:03:05.181 --> 00:03:06.204
nu,

00:03:06.261 --> 00:03:09.455
azoy durkh oyvn aropnemen vaser?

00:03:09.455 --> 00:03:12.966
zey hobn genemen dort shtriklekh mit rimen fun ⟨di⟩ hoyzn,

00:03:12.966 --> 00:03:17.817
un m'hot aropgelozt a kesl, un biz m'hot es aroyfgenemen iz shoyn geven halb kesl.

00:03:17.817 --> 00:03:22.995
dortn keyner hot keyn vaser nisht gehat. m'iz aroyfgefaln. iker, kh'hob shoyn gehat a kap vaser.

00:03:23.811 --> 00:03:29.576
 un dernokh dem hot er nokh epes geredt dortn mitn bruder. mir fleg'mir tomed dermonen dem daytsh

00:03:29.599 --> 00:03:32.431
ven mir ze'mir zikh tsunoyfgekumen. zogt er...

00:03:32.431 --> 00:03:38.978
⟨⟩, un dernokh dem z- hot men zey gegibn esn dortn. nu, zey zenen geforn in vareme vagonen mit froyen,

00:03:38.978 --> 00:03:42.449
mit, ikh veys, VOENN⟨e⟩ zenen zey geven ongetun.

00:03:42.449 --> 00:03:47.492
iz, zenen zey tsu- iz er gegan un hot g- azoy er hot POLUCH-, bakumen dos esn,

00:03:47.492 --> 00:03:49.770
 hot er gegibn a geshrey nokh a mol,

00:03:49.770 --> 00:03:52.335
un hot mir gegibn a halb broyt

00:03:52.335 --> 00:03:55.192
mit, ikh gedenk nisht, kolbas tsi fleysh.

00:03:55.232 --> 00:03:58.722
ikh gedenk nokh haynt voser a mitsve er hot gehat.

00:03:58.722 --> 00:04:00.947
un hot gekukt, oyf mir,

00:04:01.797 --> 00:04:07.014
 un hot alts oysgefregt, vifl yor ikh bin alt, vifl dos. "SCHADE, SCHAD⟨E⟩."

00:04:07.014 --> 00:04:10.987
un drum iz undzer p-, poyezd avekgegan frier far zeyerer.

00:04:11.078 --> 00:04:14.362
gedenk ikh vi haynt vi er hot undz gezogt.

00:04:14.790 --> 00:04:20.980
z-, azoy ⟨ot o⟩ hot er mir gemakht. ikh volt im haynt oykh derkent, nor vos? s'iz geven shoyn a mentsh in mitldike yorn.

00:04:20.980 --> 00:04:26.740
zogt er, "a gliklekhe rayze tsu HAUSE!" ikh hob daytsh nokh nisht farshtanen, nit gevust,

00:04:26.740 --> 00:04:29.021
nor dos hob ikh gedenkt ale yorn:

00:04:29.021 --> 00:04:31.695
a mentsh, az er tut i guts i shlekhts.

00:04:31.695 --> 00:04:33.059
guts geton.

00:04:33.100 --> 00:04:35.496
nisht ale zenen geven azoy.

00:04:35.496 --> 00:04:37.283
nu, dos iz geven fun oyvn,

00:04:37.283 --> 00:04:39.635
az me darf oyshargenen di yidn un shoyn.

00:04:39.635 --> 00:04:42.324
ze'mir gekumen tsu forn in dem Tultshin.

00:04:43.883 --> 00:04:44.909
dortn,

00:04:44.909 --> 00:04:46.813
a glik vos s'iz geven zumer,

00:04:47.005 --> 00:04:49.530
nor shreklekh. in barakn

00:04:50.008 --> 00:04:52.207
z⟨e'm-⟩ hot men undz arayngetribn,

00:04:52.207 --> 00:04:53.642
un in di barakn

00:04:53.642 --> 00:04:57.714
iz azoy ⟨ot o⟩, eyner ibern andern iz geven azoy, polkes.

00:04:58.007 --> 00:05:00.532
oyfzetsn hostu dikh nisht gekent.

00:05:00.707 --> 00:05:02.882
host dikh nisht gekent aniderzetsn.

00:05:02.882 --> 00:05:05.561
az du host gevolt, host nor azoy zikh gedarft araynrukn.

00:05:06.883 --> 00:05:11.720
un m'hot ongetribn mentshn dort fil. iker, mir ho'mir ongehoybn geyn oyf der arbet.

00:05:12.672 --> 00:05:15.271
nu, mikh hot men moyre gehat ibertsu-

00:05:17.262 --> 00:05:18.977
ibertsulozn oyf a minut,

00:05:19.438 --> 00:05:25.248
vayl ikh bin shoyn geven azoy, a meydl a untergevaksen⟨e un ale⟩. yeder fleg mikh fregn, fleg ikh zogn

00:05:25.248 --> 00:05:29.700
az ikh bin a kind. "ikh bin nokh a kind." un me fleg lakhn az m'hot mikh gezen.

00:05:29.700 --> 00:05:33.186
yeder fleg kukn oyf mir; ikh bin geven azoy a,

00:05:33.208 --> 00:05:37.904
a meydl a sheyns. kh'hob gehat sheyne hor shvartse un ales. fleg yeder

00:05:37.904 --> 00:05:42.748
zikh opshteln. iz, di shvester mayne fleg mikh nit oplozn oyf a minut,

00:05:42.748 --> 00:05:45.555
vayl s'iz geven d⟨ort⟩ groyse umglikes. flegn

00:05:45.662 --> 00:05:47.799
araynkumen daytshn,

00:05:48.328 --> 00:05:51.614
 un Rumener. m'hot oysgekloybn di shenste meydlekh.

00:05:51.614 --> 00:05:55.303
m'hot gemakht fun zey khoyzek. me fleg zey aveknemen oyf gantse nekht

00:05:55.303 --> 00:05:58.374
un teg, un drum flegn zey kumen. s'iz geven

00:05:58.374 --> 00:05:59.454
shreklekh.

00:05:59.454 --> 00:06:01.850
fleg ikh geyn mit zey oyf der arbet.

00:06:01.850 --> 00:06:04.877
dortn fleg men shteyn in vaser azoy ⟨ot o⟩,

00:06:05.170 --> 00:06:07.239
un gegrobn dem torf.

00:06:07.853 --> 00:06:10.398
der torf iz geven blote shtiker.

00:06:10.398 --> 00:06:11.841
hot men gegrobn,

00:06:11.841 --> 00:06:16.067
un drum fleg men aroysnemen, un me fleg oyf di tatshkes

00:06:16.067 --> 00:06:19.844
tsunoyfleygn tsigelekh, zey zoln zikh oystrikenen oyf der zun.

00:06:20.560 --> 00:06:22.236
fleg ikh geyn mit zey.

00:06:22.236 --> 00:06:26.330
zey hobn, m'hot getrogn, fleg ikh zitsn ⟨un⟩ tsunoyfleygn di tsigl.

00:06:26.330 --> 00:06:30.150
oykhet di hentelekh kleyne, nas⟨e i⟩n blote,

00:06:30.150 --> 00:06:31.725
un di fis.

00:06:32.490 --> 00:06:37.833
un ⟨ikh⟩ fleg zitsn ⟨un⟩ tsunoyfleygn. esn, vos fleg men do gibn? eyn mol in tog

00:06:38.110 --> 00:06:40.452
fleg men kokhn mamelige,

00:06:40.452 --> 00:06:42.789
azoy ⟨ot o⟩ oysgisn oyf a,

00:06:42.789 --> 00:06:46.031
 nu, oyf a,...

00:06:46.632 --> 00:06:47.824
oyf a plats?

00:06:47.307 --> 00:06:49.292
 oyf a lokshn-bret azoy.

00:06:47.948 --> 00:06:50.086
oyf a lokshn-bret. UNK.

00:06:49.973 --> 00:06:52.729
un di mamelige iz geven gekokht shiter,

00:06:52.729 --> 00:06:57.259
az ⟨se⟩ zol, az s'hot zikh oysgekilt, hot men gekent opnemen kvadratne shtiklekh.

00:06:57.259 --> 00:07:01.495
fleg men gibn kvadratne shtikl mamelige; dos iz geven ibern gantsn tog.

00:07:01.495 --> 00:07:05.121
un me fleg gibn, eynike mol, ferdn-fleysh,

00:07:05.245 --> 00:07:07.022
a shtikl ferdn-fleysh.

00:07:07.022 --> 00:07:10.779
nu, ven me zogt nit az s'iz ferdn-fleysh, efsher volt es yeder geke-

00:07:10.779 --> 00:07:15.086
eynike flegn esn. nu, ikh ken... ober avade iz nisht ⟨GDE⟩...

00:07:13.243 --> 00:07:14.023
ver,

00:07:14.023 --> 00:07:16.595
ver hot aykh dos esn derlangt?

00:07:17.108 --> 00:07:21.070
nu, dortn, vu m'hot gegrobn, se fleg zayn eyner

00:07:21.070 --> 00:07:22.842
vos er hot geredt daytsh

00:07:22.842 --> 00:07:27.212
un fleg shrayen dortn ⟨u⟩n, UNK dortn mit alemen.

00:07:27.212 --> 00:07:28.610
iz, ⟨⟩,

00:07:29.089 --> 00:07:32.527
 azoy ken men... zey hobn gedarft koyln, zey hobn gedarft ales.

00:07:32.527 --> 00:07:35.487
azoy zhe vestu arbetn az me git nisht esn?

00:07:35.487 --> 00:07:37.503
iz dos flegn zey gibn eyn mol in tog.

00:07:37.503 --> 00:07:40.763
fleg men loyfn shteyn, ⟨iz⟩ in der sho hot men gemuzt uspeyen,

00:07:40.763 --> 00:07:42.476
ven s'iz geven,

00:07:42.476 --> 00:07:47.025
onbaysn tsayt. un az nisht, hostu dos, hos- s'hot dir nisht gestayet, "ay,

00:07:47.025 --> 00:07:48.111
gey vayter."

00:07:48.111 --> 00:07:50.632
nor mir fleg'mir dort arumert,

00:07:51.516 --> 00:07:55.478
 vu undz ze'mir gevoynt in di barakes, flegn mir geyn durkhn dorf

00:07:55.478 --> 00:07:58.530
atin oyf arbet. in der fri fleg men undz traybn,

00:07:58.671 --> 00:08:01.906
un krik oyf der nakht flegn mir geyn durkhn dorf.

00:08:02.012 --> 00:08:05.299
do ho'mir shoyn, a bisl bist durkhgegan,

00:08:05.299 --> 00:08:07.780
nor m'hot gelebt derfun vos m'hot gebetn.

00:08:07.780 --> 00:08:12.683
fleg men zogn, "efsher host a LISHNIY shtikl broyt, gib. efsher hostu dos, gib."

00:08:12.683 --> 00:08:15.376
fleg ikh dort esn nor GOROKHn-broyt.

00:08:15.376 --> 00:08:18.408
GOROKHn-broyt, az kh'hob geesn, hob ikh shoyn nisht gevolt esn.

00:08:18.482 --> 00:08:23.137
zey hobn nisht gegesn. mir fleg men tomed zen, a shtikl GOROKHn-broyt, ikh zol esn.

00:08:23.137 --> 00:08:25.499
itster, az ikh ze GOROKH, ale yorn,

00:08:25.499 --> 00:08:29.401
kuk ikh oyf ⟨i⟩m nisht. azoy hob ikh zikh ongeesn mitn GOROKHn-broyt.

00:08:30.328 --> 00:08:34.147
azoy ze'mir opgeven dortn in dem, Tultshin

00:08:34.147 --> 00:08:35.418
biz in osyen.

00:08:36.488 --> 00:08:37.511
osyen.

00:08:37.669 --> 00:08:39.286
s'iz kalt gevorn.

00:08:39.286 --> 00:08:42.118
s'iz farfroyrn gevorn. yeder hot gekhapt gute

00:08:42.140 --> 00:08:46.758
shlafkeytn: der mit di fis hot shoyn nisht gekent geyn funem shteyn in vaser,

00:08:46.765 --> 00:08:48.683
un do funem esn.

00:08:49.684 --> 00:08:52.800
s'iz geven yents ruml in dem Tultshin oykhet.

00:08:53.397 --> 00:08:56.664
m'hot gemakht khoyzek fun yedn eynem:

00:08:56.704 --> 00:09:02.869
yidn, ven ze'mir gegan oyf di vegn, yidn mit di berder, fleg men nemen mit, tsigarn un zey

00:09:02.869 --> 00:09:04.326
unterreykhern.

00:09:04.602 --> 00:09:06.047
erlekhe yidn.

00:09:06.188 --> 00:09:10.086
ze'mir opgeven in dem Tultshin, iz geven same yunvar- yungvarg.

00:09:10.086 --> 00:09:10.923
yungvarg.

00:09:11.250 --> 00:09:14.204
m'hot tsunoyfgenemen un m'hot undz krikgeshikt

00:09:15.132 --> 00:09:16.495
keyn Popovets.

00:09:16.495 --> 00:09:20.070
nu, ze'mir gekumen krik keyn Popovets. hot undz di

00:09:20.070 --> 00:09:22.367
baleboste krik arayngenemen.

00:09:22.367 --> 00:09:26.198
nu, un azoy ze'mir geven. mir fleg'mir geyn in di derfer,

00:09:26.198 --> 00:09:29.826
 do betn, do arbetn,

00:09:29.826 --> 00:09:33.556
un mir ho'mir zikh ernert. un do fleg men geyn grobn,

00:09:33.556 --> 00:09:37.590
un me fleg geyn ales, abi me zol iberlebn dos shtikl tsayt.

00:09:38.132 --> 00:09:43.495
un s'iz geven biter un fintster shoyn. naket bin ikh gegan, on a por zokn,

00:09:43.495 --> 00:09:47.653
un on shukhvarg, un on gornisht. un azoy ho'mir gelebt.

00:09:47.987 --> 00:09:50.816
un dernokh dem, az m'hot shoyn ongehoybn,

00:09:51.531 --> 00:09:53.870
di daytshn, tsu antloyfn,

00:09:53.893 --> 00:09:58.781
ho'mir ersht dentsmol moyre gehat. az zey flegn zikh dervisn, ergets iz do yidn, fleg ⟨me⟩n hargenen.

00:09:58.888 --> 00:10:04.448
un, un s'iz geven shreklekh. mir fleg'mir zikh ersht dentsmol shtark bahaltn.

00:10:05.368 --> 00:10:09.327
nor mir ho'mir gehert az, se geyt ales shoyn beser,

00:10:09.385 --> 00:10:11.862
un zey geyen tsurik. iz,

00:10:11.862 --> 00:10:14.458
⟨darf men⟩ zen, me zol blaybn lebn.

00:10:14.481 --> 00:10:16.803
in a tog zogt men az vos zey

00:10:16.803 --> 00:10:18.772
zenen shoyn avek, di rusishe,

00:10:18.772 --> 00:10:22.744
 di rusishe kumen arayn. un mir loyf'mir in shtot gibn a kuk:

00:10:24.623 --> 00:10:31.193
iz do shoyn epes a tsvey rusishe, un mir gey'mir krik. iz, di baleboste veynt un zogt az di daytshn

00:10:31.193 --> 00:10:33.150
loyfn iber dem dorf,

00:10:33.150 --> 00:10:38.195
un me zukht yidn un me harget. "vuhin zent ir gegan? vos hot ir getun?

00:10:38.195 --> 00:10:43.714
 tsu vos zent ir gegan?" mir ho'mir azoy geveynt un zi gebetn, zi zol undz nit aroystraybn.

00:10:43.714 --> 00:10:46.527
un mir ho'mir zikh gebahaltn bay ir dortn vu,

00:10:46.527 --> 00:10:52.123
in a kamer ergets oyfn boydem, dort in a vinkl, in dem shtroy, tomer vet men kumen zukhn.

00:10:52.180 --> 00:10:55.692
nu, un drum iz avekgegan a shtikl tsayt, zenen zey,

00:10:56.533 --> 00:10:58.841
zenen zey take arayngekumen, di,

00:10:57.934 --> 00:10:58.957
di rusn?

00:10:58.841 --> 00:11:02.180
di rusishe. nu, azoy zenen arayngekumen,

00:11:03.672 --> 00:11:06.872
hot men nokh geshosn, s'iz ⟨g-⟩ nokh geven groyse tsores.

00:11:07.114 --> 00:11:10.382
undz ho'mir zikh oysgebahaltn dortn nokh

00:11:10.810 --> 00:11:13.425
a sakh, un dernokh dem hot zi gezogt,

00:11:13.442 --> 00:11:18.408
ho'mir ge-, iz gevorn a prikaz, ven s'iz shoyn geven POLNOST'YU di

00:11:18.408 --> 00:11:22.129
rusishe, hobn zey gezogt az me zol nemen un me zol,

00:11:22.129 --> 00:11:24.425
 m'hot farnemen in der ARMII

00:11:24.597 --> 00:11:26.173
mayne brider.

00:11:26.790 --> 00:11:30.267
men hot zey farnumen, ⟨ah, ⟩ far zelners?

00:11:28.478 --> 00:11:30.581
rusisher ARMII.

00:11:30.267 --> 00:11:32.285
in, in di rusishe ⟨ARMII⟩.

00:11:30.925 --> 00:11:33.562
 yo. nor s'hot nisht gedoyert keyn sakh;

00:11:33.562 --> 00:11:35.967
zenen tsugegan biz,

00:11:35.967 --> 00:11:38.529
Kamenits-Podolsk, hot men zey umgekert.

00:11:38.890 --> 00:11:41.941
m'hot opgezogt az di vos zenen in di lagers

00:11:41.941 --> 00:11:43.560
zol men nisht nemen,

00:11:43.560 --> 00:11:45.614
derfar vos,

00:11:45.614 --> 00:11:48.275
zey zoln zikh forn aheym, un fun der heym vet men nemen.

00:11:48.930 --> 00:11:51.475
nu, zenen mir opgeven nokh dortn...

00:11:51.475 --> 00:11:54.590
vifl zol ikh zogn? biz s'iz varem gevorn.

00:11:55.073 --> 00:11:56.976
nu, di baleboste,

00:11:56.976 --> 00:12:00.807
nu, PU- loz di erd ir zayn gring.

00:12:00.807 --> 00:12:03.237
zi hot undz zeyer fil geholfn.

00:12:03.237 --> 00:12:08.582
hot zi gezogt, un hot azoy geveynt ven ikh bin avekgef- ze'mir gegan, avekgeforn,

00:12:08.582 --> 00:12:11.287
un hot gezogt az ikh zol blaybn ir kind.

00:12:11.287 --> 00:12:16.138
zi hot ge- geheysn az zi iz a raykhe dort: zi hot a gortn, a shtub,

00:12:16.138 --> 00:12:18.323
mit alemen. zogt zi, "blayb!

00:12:18.323 --> 00:12:22.702
blayb! ikh'l dir shenken dem gortn, ikh'l dir khasene makhn, ikh'l dir ales."

00:12:22.702 --> 00:12:24.803
zog ikh, "ikh bin dokh a yidishke.

00:12:24.803 --> 00:12:25.732
un,

00:12:25.732 --> 00:12:30.352
azoy zhe...?" zogt zi, "vos du vest veln, vestu zayn, abi blayb." zog ikh, "neyn."

00:12:31.312 --> 00:12:32.827
 UNK...

00:12:31.455 --> 00:12:33.392
vi iz geven ir nomen?

00:12:33.345 --> 00:12:34.874
 YUZYA.

00:12:35.269 --> 00:12:37.187
nokh der milkhome,

00:12:38.586 --> 00:12:42.351
 s'iz avekgegan a tsvey yor, ze'mir gekumen tsu zikh,

00:12:42.508 --> 00:12:45.219
iz teykef ze'mir geforn atin tsu tsu.

00:12:46.086 --> 00:12:52.239
mir ho'mir dort opgeSNIMAET in dem kolkhoz vu mir ho'mir d- farloyrn dos shenste un dos beste,

00:12:52.347 --> 00:12:54.214
un vu m'hot zikh gemutshet,

00:12:54.321 --> 00:12:58.382
vu undz ze'mir geven, az undzere kinder zoln nokh a mol zen

00:12:58.459 --> 00:13:04.068
vos m'hot getun mit mentshn, un zoln nisht fargesn, un zeyere kindskinder dos zogn.

00:13:04.092 --> 00:13:07.680
ho'mir teykef opgeSNIMAET, un ikh hob dos bild.

00:13:07.838 --> 00:13:11.209
un mir fleg'mir, ze'mir geforn atin tsu tsu,

00:13:11.209 --> 00:13:14.753
derfar vos s'iz geven groyse masn-griber⟨s⟩ tsvey,

00:13:14.753 --> 00:13:17.284
un ⟨a s-⟩ shtark a sakh mentshn,

00:13:17.284 --> 00:13:22.124
un der kolkhoz, azoy ⟨zey zenen⟩ arayngekumen krik, di rusishe hobn ongehoybn grobn di erd.

00:13:22.215 --> 00:13:24.768
ho'mir moyre gehat, me zol dort nisht tsegrobn.

00:13:24.768 --> 00:13:28.742
ze'mir zikh tsunoyfgenemen, vifl s'iz geblibn, etlekhe kinder,

00:13:28.742 --> 00:13:33.290
genemen tsvey mashinen, ze'mir arayngeforn, arayngegan in kolkhoz.

00:13:33.290 --> 00:13:34.678
d⟨i⟩,

00:13:34.720 --> 00:13:38.100
dortn hobn zey gevust az s'iz azoyns do geven,

00:13:38.100 --> 00:13:41.069
az mentshn zenen oysgeshtorbn un ales,

00:13:41.069 --> 00:13:42.645
un mir ho'mir gebetn,

00:13:42.972 --> 00:13:45.396
me zol undz gibn helf, un mir zol'mir,

00:13:45.672 --> 00:13:49.195
far undzer gelt, mir zol'mir OGORO- arummakhn

00:13:49.195 --> 00:13:52.275
shtakhetn azoy, do vu s'iz di tsvey masn-griber,

00:13:52.275 --> 00:13:54.182
un zey zoln nisht grobn mer.

00:13:54.182 --> 00:13:56.246
un mir ho'mir dort ongeshribn

00:13:57.602 --> 00:14:02.528
az, vifl mentshn s'iz do un vi azoy zey zenen geshtorbn,

00:14:02.528 --> 00:14:06.658
farmutshete mentshn un ales, un flegn mir ale yor atin forn

00:14:06.715 --> 00:14:08.333
un zen,

00:14:08.333 --> 00:14:12.075
 d- oyf di pletser flegn mir geyn,

00:14:12.300 --> 00:14:15.057
ontsindn likht, haltn yidishkeyt.

00:14:15.057 --> 00:14:17.503
un di mentshn vos hobn undz gut getun

00:14:17.503 --> 00:14:19.680
flegn mir keyn mol nisht fargesn.

00:14:19.680 --> 00:14:22.802
ze'mir geforn, flegn mir onnemen fule mashinen

00:14:22.802 --> 00:14:24.758
mit,

00:14:26.104 --> 00:14:29.228
mit geshenken zey gibn ⟨un⟩,

00:14:29.228 --> 00:14:35.196
 vayl zey hobn gemeynt dentsmol az undz ze'mir VOOBSCHE epes nisht keyn mentshn. vos iz dos far a mentshn, vos zey zitsn

00:14:35.196 --> 00:14:37.488
un me tut zey azoyns un zey shvaygn?

00:14:38.826 --> 00:14:45.217
flegn mir ale yor forn. geforn farn avekforn ater, oykh geven dort oyf der erd, oyf der...

00:14:47.434 --> 00:14:56.017
un shtark a shlekhtn shikzal hob ikh gehat, UNK, aza milkhome iberlebn un azoy zen mit di oygn vos ikh hob gezen.

00:14:56.175 --> 00:14:59.787
nu, itster, danken got, ⟨kh'- b-⟩

00:14:59.787 --> 00:15:02.811
bin krank ale yorn fun dem lager

00:15:03.752 --> 00:15:09.005
un funem BRYUSHNOY tif. kh'hob opgelebt ale yorn un leb oyf shtrenge dyetes, un nisht

00:15:09.005 --> 00:15:14.732
gegesn azoy ⟨vi⟩ mentshn un nisht, gornisht vi mentshn, nor azoy leb ikh.

00:15:16.054 --> 00:15:17.148
froy Lipis,

00:15:17.148 --> 00:15:19.997
kh'volt gevolt visn az, hot ir,

00:15:20.222 --> 00:15:26.960
hot men aykh gezogt, ir zolt trogn a, a mogn-doved, dos heyst, dem JUDEN-shtern vos di DEUTSCHn hobn...

00:15:26.960 --> 00:15:28.400
ir hot dos GEHABT?

00:15:27.850 --> 00:15:30.662
ven undz ze'mir in Sukeran,

00:15:31.039 --> 00:15:33.669
iz mayn,

00:15:33.669 --> 00:15:38.566
 fleg geyn mit dermit, mayn bruder. ikh fleg in ergets nit aroysgeyn, gezesn in shtub.

00:15:38.566 --> 00:15:41.637
un er, az er iz aroysgegan, hot men gemuzt geyn mit dermit.

00:15:41.637 --> 00:15:43.708
iz gegan mitn mogn-doved.

00:15:43.948 --> 00:15:51.994
a altn pidzhak hot er epes getrofn, nor azoy hot men ongetun, ⟨hot,⟩ azoy hot men nisht getort aroy- oy! vifl m'hot im geshlogn, geharget!

00:15:51.994 --> 00:15:59.929
az er fleg aroysgeyn zen epes oyf tsu esn, fleg er aheymkumen blo! tsu tsvantsik nagaykes. vos m'hot gevolt hot men...

00:16:00.149 --> 00:16:03.281
un azoy fleg er loyfn; anisht volt'mir geven oysgeshtorbn.

00:16:05.076 --> 00:16:06.335
ven ir z-...

00:16:05.228 --> 00:16:08.496
shtark geven a shreklekh shtikl tsayt.

00:16:09.700 --> 00:16:13.907
un far vos nor oyf di yidn iz dos geven, veys ikh nisht.

00:16:14.037 --> 00:16:15.550
un itstert...

00:16:16.298 --> 00:16:22.700
fun, fun Popovets zent ir s- gegangen tsurik aheym keyn NOWOSELITZA.

00:16:21.782 --> 00:16:27.948
fun Popovets ze'mir geforn keyn Ko- Kopaygorod. dortn iz a stantsye geven,

00:16:22.700 --> 00:16:24.105
vi hot zikh dos...

00:16:27.948 --> 00:16:29.364
in Popovets nisht.

00:16:29.364 --> 00:16:32.055
un mir ho'mir zikh oyfgezetst oyf a vagon:

00:16:32.055 --> 00:16:37.514
vi, voser s'iz geven, mit V- mit VOENN⟨e⟩, mit vos, ⟨zey⟩ zenen geforn oyfn front.

00:16:37.514 --> 00:16:40.333
mir ho'mir uspeyet arayn. ze'mir arayn,

00:16:40.333 --> 00:16:43.309
⟨un⟩ ze'mir geforn biz keyn, Lipkan.

00:16:44.108 --> 00:16:49.091
un fun dortn ze'mir, geven a bisl in Lipkan. drum ze'mir avekgeforn keyn Tshernovits.

00:16:49.091 --> 00:16:50.984
in Tshernovits iz,

00:16:50.984 --> 00:16:52.708
ikh bin gegan in shkole.

00:16:52.815 --> 00:16:54.159
kh'hob gelernt.

00:16:54.385 --> 00:16:58.575
un, di shvester flegn arbetn. i eyne, i di andere

00:16:58.575 --> 00:17:00.330
hot ongehoybn arbetn.

00:17:00.330 --> 00:17:03.882
un drum ze'mir ibergeforn, zi hot khasene gehat, keyn Novoselits.

00:17:03.882 --> 00:17:09.102
bin ikh mit der klenerer geforn keyn Novoselits un ikh hob dort oykh gikh khasene gehat.

00:17:09.102 --> 00:17:11.055
ikh hob shtark yung khasene gehat,

00:17:11.055 --> 00:17:13.456
nokh keyn nayntsn yor nisht alt geven.

00:17:13.456 --> 00:17:17.456
mayn man iz geven alt dray un tsvontsik, oykhet nisht shtark...

00:17:17.148 --> 00:17:20.314
er iz oykhet geven fun NOWOSELITZA?

00:17:19.047 --> 00:17:24.723
er iz fun Novoselits geven, un hot gehat shtark a bitern lager oykh.

00:17:24.723 --> 00:17:27.153
nisht eyn mol iz dem, dem foter,

00:17:27.153 --> 00:17:31.943
hot men ongegibn az er iz a komunist. Avrom, hot er geheysn, Lipis.

00:17:31.982 --> 00:17:37.173
iz, hot men im opgeshlogn di lungen. m'hot im azoy lang geshlogn un er iz geshtorbn.

00:17:38.344 --> 00:17:41.808
shtark, ⟨,⟩ shreklekh geven, un fun zeyer,

00:17:41.808 --> 00:17:46.677
zenen geven shtark a s- a groyse familye, un m'iz geblibn zeyer vintsik.

00:17:46.677 --> 00:17:49.560
er iz mit der muter aheymgekumen mit der shvester.

00:17:49.566 --> 00:17:51.799
nu, di shvester iz geven

00:17:51.799 --> 00:17:53.110
gut gut,

00:17:53.110 --> 00:17:57.592
un der lager hot zikh, vayzt oys, ongerufn: bay zibn un draysik yor iz zi geshtorbn.

00:17:59.353 --> 00:18:00.899
ven hot ir...

00:17:59.771 --> 00:18:03.060
un er hot ⟨in⟩... nayn un fertsik yor.

00:18:03.960 --> 00:18:08.487
hot zeyer fil mitgem- er fleg zingen azoyne lider funem lager.

00:18:08.487 --> 00:18:12.133
dortn in lager fleg men tsunoyfshteln yidishe lider,

00:18:12.133 --> 00:18:14.704
shtark sheyne un ⟨TRAUR⟩ike.

00:18:15.013 --> 00:18:17.288
 un er hot gekent shtark sheyn zingen.

00:18:17.288 --> 00:18:21.878
ikh gedenk zey nisht. kh'hob oykhet gevust, un di kinder hobn eynike rusishe gevust.

00:18:21.878 --> 00:18:23.101
zey hobn fargesn.

00:18:23.101 --> 00:18:28.257
fl- ikh fleg zogn, "me darf nisht, dermonen zikh. me darf nisht. se kost mikh gezunt."

00:18:28.257 --> 00:18:29.842
fleg im nisht lozn.

00:18:29.842 --> 00:18:32.416
nor er hot gekent zeyer fil lider.

00:18:32.416 --> 00:18:35.024
dortn fleg men zingen di lider,

00:18:35.024 --> 00:18:38.295
azoy m'hot, geharget un azoy di, di

00:18:38.368 --> 00:18:43.115
SHUTSMANY mit di NEMTSn zenen arayn in lager, un vos m'hot geton.

00:18:43.115 --> 00:18:48.218
er hot gekent zeyer fil, nor ⟨er iz⟩, er iz geven in der zayt fun Bershad.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:54.401
shtark shver⟨n⟩ hobn zey gehat. ales oysgeshtorbn, a groyse mishpokhe geven.

00:18:55.108 --> 00:18:59.574
ve- ven hot ir ⟨khase- genah-⟩ khasene gehat? in velkhn yor?

00:18:58.134 --> 00:19:00.114
,

00:19:00.964 --> 00:19:02.412
 velkhn yor?

00:19:02.412 --> 00:19:06.094
UNK az ikh bin geven alt... ze, vos ikh veys shoyn nisht keyn...

00:19:04.710 --> 00:19:08.096
zent geven alt nayntsn yor, hot ir gezogt frieret?

00:19:06.690 --> 00:19:11.707
nayntsn, DA. UNK tsvey un draysik un, nayntsn...

00:19:12.439 --> 00:19:13.744
yo, s'iz

00:19:13.617 --> 00:19:14.947
..

00:19:13.744 --> 00:19:14.762
in...

00:19:15.342 --> 00:19:21.866
UNK men darf itst nikh- rekh- nisht rekhenen; me veys shoyn vi, ven ir hot gehat nayntsn yor, veys men vos...

00:19:20.456 --> 00:19:22.738
nayntsn yor bin ikh alt geven.

00:19:22.738 --> 00:19:25.376
nu, dos hob ikh khotsh gehat glik:

00:19:25.399 --> 00:19:28.838
a man zeyer a voyl⟨er⟩, un er hot mikh lib gehat.

00:19:28.838 --> 00:19:31.682
un s'iz bay undz geven aza familye,

00:19:31.682 --> 00:19:36.519
vos undz ⟨ho⟩'mir gevoynt in a kleyn shtetl, vos yeder fleg undz mekane zayn.

00:19:36.216 --> 00:19:40.901
dos iz NOWOSELITZA vayter geven? di shtot vos ir zent geboyrn ⟨gevorn⟩?

00:19:38.136 --> 00:19:39.250
yo.

00:19:39.250 --> 00:19:43.444
un di kinder mayne oysgelernt. zey hobn zeyer gut gelernt,

00:19:43.444 --> 00:19:46.571
un drum zenen zey geforn keyn Moskve shtudirn,

00:19:46.628 --> 00:19:47.975
un m'hot beyde...

00:19:47.975 --> 00:19:50.404
di tokhter iz a dokter,

00:19:50.404 --> 00:19:52.771
a ⟨ts-⟩ a tseyn-ARZT,

00:19:52.771 --> 00:19:57.382
un der zun hot gearbet in institut. er iz a ELEKTRONSHCHIK,

00:19:57.382 --> 00:20:00.723
a PROGRAMMIST. itster arbet er oykh shoyn do

00:20:00.723 --> 00:20:03.424
PROGRAMMIST, un fardint zeyer gut.

00:20:03.424 --> 00:20:05.921
 shtark voyle kinder, un

00:20:05.921 --> 00:20:09.541
ales iz geven gut, nor dos lebn iz bay mir geven a bisl kurts,

00:20:09.541 --> 00:20:11.971
un dos vos ale yorn bin ikh krank.

00:20:11.971 --> 00:20:15.933
nor az kh'hob ibergelebt azoyns, iz oykhet danken got.

00:20:16.918 --> 00:20:19.629
ir hot oykhet geARBEIT,...?

00:20:18.640 --> 00:20:21.075
ale yorn hob ikh gearbet.

00:20:21.075 --> 00:20:24.467
nisht gezesn. fertsik yor hob ikh opgearbet,

00:20:24.467 --> 00:20:26.593
un gekhovet tsvey kinder oykh.

00:20:26.593 --> 00:20:29.538
gearbet a bukhhaltershe ale yorn.

00:20:29.538 --> 00:20:32.488
oyf eyn plats, eyn un draysik yor.

00:20:33.777 --> 00:20:35.593
hob ikh opgearbet.

00:20:36.207 --> 00:20:40.464
un drum hobn di kinder gezogt, me darf forn ater. forn, forn.

00:20:40.510 --> 00:20:43.645
mir iz shoyn alts eyns, abi zey zol zayn gut.

00:20:43.645 --> 00:20:47.088
un kh'hob moyre gehat shtark far di MESTNe mentshn,

00:20:47.088 --> 00:20:52.501
zey zoln nisht tun nokh a mol ot dos vos zey hobn getun a mol mit undz. di MESTNe dortn...

00:20:52.508 --> 00:20:55.370
ven undz ze'mir geven zayn in lager

00:20:55.370 --> 00:20:57.787
do in Novoselits un do arum,

00:20:57.787 --> 00:20:59.826
volt keyn eyner nisht geven geblibn lebn.

00:21:00.405 --> 00:21:03.785
nor dortn iz gebidevete mentshn geven,

00:21:03.785 --> 00:21:05.327
un zey flegn helfn.

00:21:05.670 --> 00:21:09.338
der hot gegibn a tepl milekh, der hot gegibn a shtikl broyt,

00:21:09.338 --> 00:21:14.219
vifl zey hobn gekent. zey hobn dokh nisht gekent undz hodeven; s'iz geven in tsayt fun der milkhome ⟨un s'iz⟩ geven shver.

00:21:14.631 --> 00:21:15.604
nu...

00:21:17.483 --> 00:21:21.830
vos k- vos klert ir, froy Lipis, vos hot es gemakht

00:21:21.921 --> 00:21:22.905
oyf aykh,

00:21:22.905 --> 00:21:27.511
az ir hot alts dos ibergelebt un ir zent a kind geven,

00:21:27.511 --> 00:21:32.394
ven ir hot gezen un derlebt al di zakhn, vos ir hot geredt UNK?

00:21:31.523 --> 00:21:33.187
itster vil ikh

00:21:33.413 --> 00:21:40.022
az, kinder, mayne kinder veln zeyer gut gedenken, vayl zey hobn zeyer fil gehert derfun.

00:21:40.095 --> 00:21:43.511
zey hobn gehert; der foter fleg tomed dertseyln,

00:21:43.511 --> 00:21:45.112
ikh, di bobe.

00:21:45.112 --> 00:21:50.242
u- un az mayne kinder un mayne kindskinder veysn shoyn oykh derfun.

00:21:50.242 --> 00:21:55.842
un di vos veln geboyrn vern zoln visn vos s'iz forgekumen, vos mentshn hobn iberlebt,

00:21:55.842 --> 00:21:58.779
az azoyns zol shoyn mer keyn mol nisht forkumen.

00:21:58.894 --> 00:22:00.960
ot dos zog ikh.

00:22:02.809 --> 00:22:03.815
froy Lipis,

00:22:04.210 --> 00:22:06.263
s'iz nokh efsher epes

00:22:04.277 --> 00:22:05.094
y-

00:22:06.370 --> 00:22:09.328
vos ikh HAB- kh'hob nisht gefregt bay aykh,

00:22:09.255 --> 00:22:11.629
 veys ikh, ikh, bay mir,

00:22:09.328 --> 00:22:11.729
vos ikh hob poshet nisht gefregt?

00:22:11.629 --> 00:22:15.740
hob ikh gehat letstns shtark a shvere operatsye. iz fun dem NARKOZ,

00:22:15.740 --> 00:22:18.446
iz ⟨az,⟩ shtark gedenk ikh nisht.

00:22:18.520 --> 00:22:21.755
azoy az antshuldikt, efsher hob ikh epes, ⟨⟩,

00:22:20.899 --> 00:22:27.373
neyn, ikh freg nor tsi, iz epes vos ir volt dertseyln, un ikh hob poshet nisht gefregt aykh?

00:22:22.013 --> 00:22:23.952
nisht azoy...

00:22:26.667 --> 00:22:31.170
neyn, ikh veys, ikh farges, letstns shtark.

00:22:31.345 --> 00:22:36.587
fun zint kh'hob gehat di operatsye, gedenk ikh zeyer shvakh., kon zayn az kh'hob epes

00:22:36.627 --> 00:22:40.614
n- aykh nisht azoy dertseylt. ikh fleg zogn, ven me lozt mikh zitsn

00:22:40.614 --> 00:22:41.947
teg un nekht,

00:22:41.947 --> 00:22:44.588
volt m⟨UNK⟩ nisht geKHVATIT, ikh zol dertseyln.

00:22:44.440 --> 00:22:45.952
kh'vil aykh zogn...

00:22:44.588 --> 00:22:48.517
az kh'hob gezogt az ikh vil nor a shtikl broyt mikh ontsuesn, a kind,

00:22:48.557 --> 00:22:50.171
vos iz nokh erger?

00:22:50.869 --> 00:22:54.409
un zen azoyne umglikn un tsores, vi me ligt un me shtarbt

00:22:54.409 --> 00:22:56.786
un me ken gornisht helfn, un.

00:22:57.552 --> 00:23:00.086
ir hot takesh, froy Lipis, dertseylt

00:23:00.086 --> 00:23:02.881
zeyer az mir, az me farshteyt dos.

00:23:02.881 --> 00:23:07.000
mir veln itst makh- mir veln itst opru- ir vet zikh opruen itst a bisele,

00:23:02.915 --> 00:23:04.338
ikh veys.

00:23:06.685 --> 00:23:09.181
neyn, ikh'l aykh vayzn di kartes.

00:23:07.000 --> 00:23:08.401
